{{Infobox dungeon |name = Iron Island |image = [[File:Iron Island.png|300px]] |caption = An outside view of Iron Island. |tokens = 66,500 |location = The southernmost island off the northwestern coast of Sinnoh. }} '''Iron Island''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Sinnoh]]. It initially has 64 tiles arranged in an 8x8 square, including 8 chest tiles, 19 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
